plex storyline and such and also includes many things that may be offensive to others, but also has many many issues discussed within it...like power corrupts, racism, etc. <br>
<br>
This a 5 part story, i.e. 5 games. Each take place in seperate times, but they flow into one another, even though some they take place thousands of years apart. This also takes place in a world of my own creation with my own mytholog and such. <br>
<br>
Part 1: The Dragon God War. This story tells of the tale of the War of the Seven Dragon Gods, of Niemez Raziel with the power of his other 5 bothers against Darusic Raziel. What happens pretty much is that Niemez and 5 brothers believe at their brother, Darusic, will kill them and end up causing havoc upon the world. They elect Niemez to fight him, but he is too weak and must get the power of his brothers to help him. Each turn into a peice of armor or orb or something that has all of their power within it, giving their life so that niemez can win. In the end Darusic fears death by his brother and goes into hiding...<br>
<br>
Part 2 (unneeded part but is part of the story): After many years Darusic has a son and has become a very wicked god. He has killed his love, Lady Velin, and tried to raise his son, Kino Raziel, but Velin sent him to a far off place never to be seen by his father again at a ver young age. Kino has grown up to become a very powerful assassin. He gets a job from a mysterious ma and while taking on the job finds that that man is his father and what really happened all those years ago. Kino then through anger and such goes after Niemez and kills him eventually.<br>
<br>
Part 3: Ciery Hadespyre starts to hate everything, but most of all, half-breeds. He soon finds sympathizers and joins a group out to kill all half-breeds. He soon finds out though that he is a Dragoon, which is a half-breed even as little as it is, and he has to make the choice of whether to stay with the group hide his identity or leave and fight against them. the group ends up finding out an ancient legends of an orb or something that allows races to breed or merge together through it's power alone. They set out on findig it and eventually find it. A battle ensues when they get to it and whether or not Cieryn is with them they win and he dies. (side note: the Dragon Spirit within him is Darusic Raziel from the first story...quite ironic that his hiding place turns t his death bed.)<br>
<br>
Part 4: A war breaks out after the 3rd story over who did it. A hero known as Dyne arises and ends the war.<br>
<br>
Part 5: Years upon years later when all the rest of the story has been forgotten and what hasn't is myth, a group of youth uncover the truth of all that happened and through some unknown means unlock a Demon that ravages the planet. Eventually the youth are the only ones able to stop it with their knowledge, but by that time all but a few humans are left. This all leads into the modern real world that we live and explains why we have all these myths of creatures like elves.<br>
<br>
The story is told in a different order however because i think it's beter that way. the first part that is told is the 3rd part and then the first and then the 5th part with the 2nd and 4th parts following.<br>
<br>
